content:
Ukrainian Army Nazar Chepurny took Gold at the World Gymnastics Cup, which takes place in the Azerbaijan Baku capital.

About thisinformsThe Central Sports Club of the Armed Forces.

"In the reference jump, our gymnast, showed the result 14.900 points," - the message reads.

According to the finals, the Ukrainian went by the leader of the qualifying Wai Hung Shek (14.866) from Hong Kong and British Harry Gepvort (14.866).

It should be noted that for Nazar Chepurny is the second award in the season. In February Armygot a “silver”At the World Cup in Egyptian Cairo.

As reportedArmyinform, Arthur Felfner Armachers won the gold of Europe with a spear throw.
